<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Bienvenida a tu Entorno de Desarrollo</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #4f46e5;
            --bg: #0f172a;
            --card-bg: #1e293b;
            --text: #f8fafc;
            --text-muted: #94a3b8;
            --accent: #10b981;
        }
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg);
            color: var(--text);
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 2rem;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            width: 100%;
        }
        header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }
        h1 {
            color: var(--primary);
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        .subtitle {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }
        .grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 1.5rem;
        }
        .card {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.1);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
        }
        .card h2 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: var(--accent);
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        .info-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        .info-label {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .info-value {
            font-family: 'Cascadia Code', 'Fira Code', monospace;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            padding: 0.1rem 0.4rem;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        ul {
            padding-left: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }
        li {
            margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 3rem;
            text-align: center;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
        code {
            color: #ec4899;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>¡Bienvenido a tu VM de Desarrollo!</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">Este entorno ha sido provisionado automáticamente con Packer.</p>
        </header>

        <div class="grid">
            <div class="card">
                <h2>Información del Sistema</h2>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Hostname:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">${hostname}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Usuario:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">${username}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Password:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">developer</span>
                </div>
                <p><small style="color: var(--text-muted)">* Se recomienda cambiar la contraseña con el comando <code>passwd</code></small></p>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <h2>Conectividad</h2>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Puerto SSH:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">${ssh_port}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Puerto RDP:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">3389</span>
                </div>
                <p>Puedes conectar via RDP usando el nombre:<br><code>${hostname}.local</code></p>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <h2>Herramientas Instaladas</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Docker:</strong> Engine, Compose, LazyDocker</li>
                    <li><strong>Git:</strong> CLI, LazyGit, GitHub CLI</li>
                    %{ if install_vscode == "true" }<li><strong>VS Code:</strong> Con extensiones básicas</li>%{ endif }
                    %{ if install_cursor == "true" }<li><strong>Cursor:</strong> AI-powered editor</li>%{ endif }
                    %{ if install_antigravity == "true" }<li><strong>Antigravity:</strong> Google AI IDE</li>%{ endif }
                    <li><strong>Navegador:</strong> ${install_browser}</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <h2>Atajos Útiles (Shell)</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li><code>d</code>: docker</li>
                    <li><code>dc</code>: docker compose</li>
                    <li><code>lg</code>: lazygit</li>
                    <li><code>lzd</code>: lazydocker</li>
                    <li><code>ll</code>: ls -la</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            Generado el: ${timestamp}
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
